headline: FIS Recognizes Latest Cohort at 2024 FIS Innovation Day, Showcasing the Next Generation of Tech Across the Money Lifecycle
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., December 05, 2024--Global financial technology leader FIS® (NYSE: FIS) proudly announced today the recognition of its latest cohort at the 2024 FIS Fintech Accelerator Innovation Day. Nine growth-stage fintech companies presented their technology at FIS’ Innovation Center as part of the event on November 13 to an audience of partners and banking clients, showcasing innovative solutions that aim to bring clarity and unity to the money lifecycle.
